sentence: Trump antagonist and Wyoming Rep. Liz Cheney hauled in $2 million in the last three months, a massive haul for a House race in an off-year election, and has $4.7 million in the bank.
author: Cameron Joseph
title: Trump's Favorite Candidates Are Getting Crushed in Fundraising

sentence: And on the House side, Trump gave to Harriet Hageman, who is running a primary challenge to Rep. Liz Cheney, R-Wyo.
title: Trump gave $1M to Meadows nonprofit weeks after Jan. 6 panel's creation
